    <p style="margin: 4px 0; font-size: 14px;">Founder, AnyVision Media</p>
    <p style="margin: 4px 0; font-size: 13px; color: #666;">
      <a href="https://www.anyvisionmedia.com" style="color: #FF6D5A;">www.anyvisionmedia.com</a>
